{{Top|leg|canon=Elephantine}}
A '''pachydermoid''', also known as '''pachyderm''',<ref name="NEGAS">''[[The New Essential Guide to Alien Species]]''</ref> was a type of [[Species/Legends|species]], unrelated and from separate [[Planet/Legends|planets]], members of which shared certain physical characteristics. Pachydermoids typically had either trunks or elongated mouths, thick skin, and hoof-like feet. Another typical&mdash;but not all-encompassing&mdash;trait was the possession of tusks or tusk-like [[Tooth/Legends|teeth]].{{Fact}}

A number of [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] pachydermoid species existed, as well as non-sentient species.{{Fact}}

